&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>The difference between &lt;strong>Vertex AI&lt;/strong> and &lt;strong>Google AI Studio&lt;/strong> lies in their scope, functionality, and target audiences within Google&amp;rsquo;s suite of AI tools.&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
