style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#1-vertex-ai" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Vertex AI&lt;/strong> is Google&amp;rsquo;s &lt;strong>end-to-end AI platform&lt;/strong> for machine learning (ML) and AI model development, training, deployment, and management. It is designed for developers and data scientists who want a comprehensive environment to build, deploy, and scale ML models.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Serverless databases</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/dsblog/serverless-databases/</link><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/dsblog/serverless-databases/</guid><description>&lt;p>
